node.text:
I would like to thank @canadiensmtl for 3 great years. To all the fans - I felt your support from the day I arrived. The Tomas Tataaaaar video was an amazing hit. I loved it. To my two linemates @bgally.11 and @phildanault21 . Gally - It was fun teaching you how to play 7 Up and 7 down with the bad cards you always got. To Phil - you were the first NHL teammate I had to teach to speak English. That was fun. Thank you for the great memories and your friendship. 
@njdevils I can’t wait for the puck to drop.  #letsgo

node.text:
Congrats to @shawz65 to an incredible career .Two time Stanley Cup Champ🏆🏆. Unbelievable friend and teammate . You played with passion, heart  and battled like warrior . You are such an inspiration to everyone around you. I had so much fun with you on and the off the ice. Very happy that I could teach you how to play 7 up and 7 down♣️♥️♦️♠️🃏😜
I want to wish you all the best in your retirement . 🙏

node.text:
👌🏼Very happy to announce that this season, Küto Restaurants and I will give you discounts on my special "Tuna Tatar" for each goal I score. In addition, I invite you to participate in a contest to win a dinner for 4 people courtesy of Küto with a virtual meet n greet with me on March 27th. You could also win one of the 50 pucks that I personally signed. Make sure to follow @kutotartares for details and to get the promo code after each of my goals. It will be valid for the day after the game. 😁🏒

Très heureux de vous annoncer que cette saison, les restaurants Küto vous offrirons un rabais sur mon « Tuna Tatar » à chaque but que je marquerai! De plus, je vous invite à participer au concours auquel vous pourriez gagner un souper pour 4 personnes offert par Küto en ma compagnie lors d’une rencontre virtuelle le 27 mars prochain. Vous pourriez aussi gagner l'une des 50 rondelles que j’autographierai!  Assurez-vous de suivre @kutotartares pour obtenir les détails et le code promo après chacun de mes buts valide le lendemain du match jusqu’à la fermeture des restaurants. 😁
#kutorestaurants
#montrealcanadiens #contest #mvpgroupagency #kuto #kutotartares
